headline: Ethisphere Names Paychex Among World’s Most Ethical Companies® for 17th Time
summary: ROCHESTER, N.Y., March 11, 2025--Paychex, Inc., a leading provider of integrated human capital management software solutions for human resources, employee benefits, insurance services, and payroll has once again been named one of the World’s Most Ethical Companies® by Ethisphere. This marks the 17th time Paychex has been recognized since the annual program began in 2007.
